					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I've worked on the project a bit this weekend. Movable dirt blocks are now working. When they're not moving they are displayed as background tiles. Otherwise a lot of the original levels would have to be excluded because of the NES sprite limit. Also notice that they can be moved into water and force fields etc. 
<br />
<br />You can download a demo <a href="http://home.no/johan-af/chip/chip.nes" class="postlink">here</a>.</div>

